Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the deployment and data flow of the fecgov_fec-eregs system:

```plantuml
@startuml fecgov_fec-eregs

actor Developer
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "Cloud Foundry CLI" as CF
participant "Cloud.gov" as Cloud
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
database "ElasticSearch" as ES
participant "Django App" as App
actor User

Developer -> Git: Push code
Git -> CF: Trigger deployment
CF -> Cloud: Deploy application
Cloud -> App: Start Django application
Cloud -> DB: Provision PostgreSQL
Cloud -> ES: Provision ElasticSearch
App -> DB: Initialize database
App -> ES: Initialize search index
Developer -> CF: Run load_regs task
CF -> App: Execute regulation loading
App -> DB: Store regulation data
App -> ES: Index regulation data
User -> App: Request regulation
App -> DB: Fetch regulation data
App -> ES: Search regulation (if needed)
App -> User: Display regulation

@enduml
```